        <mxCell id="5WOREspq2-OEe74p-t21-12" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;Receiver&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;The receiver operates with three functions: sendAT(), sendMsg(), and handshake().&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;SendAT(), is a debugger. It checks if the transmitter in the CanSat is working properly. SendMsg(), sends a command to receiver and raspberry, to start collecting and sending data. handshake(), is there constantly checking if the two radio modules are connected, if not, it runs sendAT() and SendMsg(), again.&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
